title: House for sale
address: დავით გარეჯელის 23, Davit Garejeli Street, Nadzaladevi District, Tbilisi
description:
House for sale in Tbilisi.
Address: 23 David Garejeli St (a five minute walk to the Grmagele metro station, 15 minutes to the Tbilisi sea).
Area of the house  140 sqm.
Total area including a garden  450 sqm.
There are mature fruit trees in the garden  grape, fig fruit, pomegranate, sour cherry, cherry, apple, pear.
The ground floor is elevated and there is a lower level underneath it. The lower level comprises three rooms with windows. The total area of the lower level is 55 sqm and it has two entrances, one from the house and the other one from the outside.
There is a mansard roof (unfinished).
Part of the house is currently let to three families. Each unit has a separate entrance, electric meter and bathroom. There is a potential to increase the number of tenants.
There is a well developed infrastructure nearby with a walking distance to schools, kindergartens, hospital, grocery stores and supermarkets.
This is a corner house, so there is an opportunity to build a multi story block of flats or a hotel on the premise. One owner open to negotiation.
Contacts in Tbilisi: +995 579 63 77 22 , +995 322 61 14 80.
Contact in Russia: +7 985 90 694 54 (watsapp, viber).
